<ul><li>Brush (I like <a href="https://www.getquip.com/" target="_blank" aria-label="Quip (opens in a new tab)" rel="noreferrer noopener">Quip</a> for this – feels good)</li><li>Floss</li><li>Washed Face</li><li>Fluency Control (this is to help control my stutter)</li><li>Created Something</li><li>Listened To Audible Book</li><li>Read On My Kindle</li></ul><p>I track a few other things that I didn’t include, but I wanted to give you a great start on ideas of things you can track. </p>



